                <h1>&#039;Our community is exhausted&#039;: Muslim student leaders explain challenges they faced working with administrators on hiring Muslim chaplain</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/1a24dc2f-c270-4879-84ee-65acce21b8b9.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;The&#x20;Office&#x20;of&#x20;Student&#x20;Affairs&#x20;recruited&#x20;the&#x20;help&#x20;of&#x20;the&#x20;Muslim&#x20;Students&#x20;Association&#x20;to&#x20;find&#x20;and&#x20;hire&#x20;a&#x20;Muslim&#x20;chaplain.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>The Office of Student Affairs recruited the help of the Muslim Students Association to find and hire a Muslim chaplain.</p>

